# MOJ Forms Tech Docs

## Who is this documentation for?
These Tech Docs are used and maintained by the MoJ Forms team and provide technical information for maintaining the services.

For more information on the product there is a [product website](https://moj-forms.service.justice.gov.uk).

## MOJ Forms Platform
